## Backend: `dead-angle-api/`

*(Multiplayer only — not contacted during singleplayer)*

```
dead-angle-api/
│
├── Controllers/
│   └── RoomsController.cs                      # POST /rooms → create room, return sessionId + roomCode
│                                               # POST /rooms/{code}/join → join room, return sessionId
│
├── Hubs/
│   └── GameHub.cs                              # SignalR hub — maps sessionId to player slot in OnConnectedAsync;
│                                               # receives player input and host start signal; emits all game events;
│                                               # detects disconnection and ends session
│
├── Services/
│   ├── GameService.cs                          # Game loop (~20Hz), player positions, projectile hit detection,
│   │                                           # round resolution, ammo lifecycle, score tracking
│   ├── RoomService.cs                          # Room lifecycle — create, join, end; session ID generation;
│   │                                           # Player1/Player2 slot assignment
│   ├── MazeGenerator.cs                        # Procedural maze generation — called when host starts and each round end
│   └── DiscordWebhookService.cs                # Outbound POST to Discord webhook on session end
│
├── Physics/
│   ├── ProjectileSimulator.cs                  # Server-side projectile simulation — authoritative hit detection only
│   └── WallReflection.cs                       # Reflection math — must stay identical to client wallReflection.ts
│
├── Models/
│   ├── Room.cs                                 # Room state — code, phase, players, scores
│   ├── Player.cs                               # Player — slot, sessionId, connectionId, position, angle, ammo count, reload state
│   ├── Projectile.cs                           # Projectile — id, position, velocity, ownerSlot, remaining lifetime (max 10s)
│   ├── MazeLayout.cs                           # Wall grid — list of wall rectangles defining the maze
│   ├── GamePhase.cs                            # Enum: Lobby, Playing, RoundTransition, Summary
│   └── PlayerSlot.cs                           # Enum: Player1, Player2
│
├── DTOs/
│   ├── RoomResponse.cs                         # { SessionId, PlayerSlot, RoomCode? } — RoomCode populated on create, null on join
│   └── Events/
│       ├── GameStartedEvent.cs                 # Emitted when host clicks Start — { maze: MazeLayout }; both clients navigate to /game
│       ├── GameTickEvent.cs                    # ~20Hz broadcast — { players: [{ slot, position, angle, ammoCount, reloading }] }
│       ├── ProjectileFiredEvent.cs             # { projectileId, ownerSlot, startPosition, angle, velocity, firedAt }
│       ├── RoundEndedEvent.cs                  # { winnerSlot, scores, newMaze: MazeLayout }
│       └── SessionEndedEvent.cs                # { finalScores } — emitted on disconnect; triggers Discord webhook server-side
│
├── Program.cs                                  # DI, SignalR, CORS, routing
├── appsettings.json
├── appsettings.Development.json
├── dead-angle-api.csproj
└── .gitignore
```